  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK837">
<l>ētilā rārat tamarpacippar pētai</l>
<l>peruñcelva muṟṟak kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a fool happens to get an immense fortune, his neighbours will enjoy it while his relations starve.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
